c agents (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/237031/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, More', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Chlorothiazide, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, More', 1767369485);
